# .zprofile - sourced once at login
#
# WARNING: Do not use login shells with these dotfiles.
# All PATH setup is in .zshenv, and all interactive config (functions,
# aliases, tool hooks) is in .zshrc. Login shells source .zprofile
# BEFORE .zshrc, which can cause duplicate PATH entries and ordering
# issues. Configure your terminal to launch non-login interactive
# shells (zsh -i, not zsh -l).
